		"description": "<p><strong>Planar Energy. </strong>Choose the type of&nbsp;planarite that serves as your primary life&nbsp;force from the following list: air, death,&nbsp;earth, fire, life, space, time, water. You&nbsp;gain resistance to a specific damage type&nbsp;based on this source.</p>\n<p>Regardless of planarite type, the&nbsp;planar energy contained within allows you&nbsp;to forgo sleep. When you take a long rest,&nbsp;you spend 4 hours in a state of inactivity&nbsp;(instead of sleeping for 6 hours). While&nbsp;powered down in this way, you suffer no&nbsp;penalty to passive Perception. A long rest&nbsp;remains 8 hours for you as normal, and&nbsp;the remainder of the time must be filled&nbsp;only with light activity.</p>\n<p><strong>TABLE: PLANARITE</strong></p>\n<table style=\"width: 50%; border-width: 1px; height: 142.375px;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col><col></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 24.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 24.7969px;\">\n<h4><strong>Planarite</strong></h4>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 24.7969px;\">\n<h4><strong>Resistance</strong></h4>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">Air</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">Thunder</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">Death</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">Necrotic</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">Earth</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">Lightning</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">Fire</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">Fire</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">Life</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">Radiant</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">Space</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">Psychic</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">Time</td>\n<td style=\"heig